    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加入人类生存之战，在 <strong>IRON GUARD: Salvation —— 一款令人振奋的塔防游戏中体验策略乐趣</strong>。建造防御，升级炮塔，并用你的无人机抵挡无情的机器人攻势。只有你的战术智慧才能在不同星球的战斗中拯救人类，包括充满敌意的<strong>阿克里斯</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >󠁪<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861410/extras/90ed6a8bfa359c5bae96496ed5f1cad1.poster.avif?t=1763661699\" width=1170 height=657 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861410/extras/90ed6a8bfa359c5bae96496ed5f1cad1.webm?t=1763661699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>英雄</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861410/extras/64a886c5f66fc2827753b101fc033b61.webp?t=1763661699\" width=1560 height=29 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >指挥英雄 —— 控制格雷夫斯、伊琳娜和米切尔，他们独特的技能能够扭转战局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861410/extras/4ccf0525445349dd21835cd55b448aaa.poster.avif?t=1763661699\" width=1170 height=518 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861410/extras/4ccf0525445349dd21835cd55b448aaa.webm?t=1763661699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>特点</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861410/extras/64a886c5f66fc2827753b101fc033b61.webp?t=1763661699\" width=1560 height=29 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861410/extras/00eed2c247032aa48bcb169c0105b444.webp?t=1763661699\" width=16 height=16 /></span> <strong>动态玩法</strong> —— 敌人会适应每一场战斗。选择难度和游戏方式：从高处指挥，或亲自操作无人机射击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >󠁪󠁪</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861410/extras/207613e0a9002d11cbed77cf82089e68.webp?t=1763661699\" width=16 height=16 /></span> <strong>多种模式与机制。</strong> 以不同方式游玩，调整每一次战斗，并登上排行榜。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >󠁪</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861410/extras/c821ee22862375ab1276bd02cf550255.webp?t=1763661699\" width=16 height=16 /></span> <strong>强大的敌人</strong> —— 独特的战术会考验你的技巧。仔细选择并组合炮塔，充分利用战场上的一切机会。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >󠁪</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861410/extras/5f511ab80393dba1b299d68400be485b.webp?t=1763661699\" width=16 height=16 /></span> <strong>升级与资源管理</strong> —— 升级炮塔和无人机；使用采集器、矿物和工厂来保证稳定的资源流。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >󠁪</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861410/extras/95482ada6791c95489d5e8ba8f140b3a.webp?t=1763661699\" width=16 height=16 /></span> <strong>战术操控</strong> —— 从高空指挥，或深入战场，沉浸在炮塔和机器的宏大世界中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >󠁪</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>军械库</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861410/extras/64a886c5f66fc2827753b101fc033b61.webp?t=1763661699\" width=1560 height=29 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从 <strong>25+ 种炮塔</strong>中挑选，<strong>移动平台</strong>调整防御，部署<strong>超级武器</strong>等。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861410/extras/0ff6182473b06e63172db1e8a30227ce.avif?t=1763661699\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>世界</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861410/extras/64a886c5f66fc2827753b101fc033b61.webp?t=1763661699\" width=1560 height=29 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>30 个手工关卡</strong>， 分布在多个星球 —— 每一关都有新的障碍和战略机遇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861410/extras/443101b02b168c11bcd148bc0005485b.avif?t=1763661699\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861410/extras/38f133f0a75699c1751a987df6e05588.poster.avif?t=1763661699\" width=1170 height=656 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861410/extras/38f133f0a75699c1751a987df6e05588.webm?t=1763661699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861410/extras/83cc37eb5035ae576699fd8744f574f7.webp?t=1763661699\" width=1560 height=29 /></span></p>",
